what is a board book example given in details i am going to get my friend a baby gift and i have choosen one of my fav books the runaway bunny by margaret wise brown when i went on barnes noble to order the book online they have three choices formats paperback hardcover or board book what is a board book a board book is a book that is usually small chunky and has thick cardboard pages anytime you decide to get your friends child a book definately go for the board books until the child is about years old another good type of book for a baby is what's called a bath book these books are made of vinyl and the pages are usually puffy on another note if you are going to buy books for your friend's baby another good book is corduroy by don freeman and good night moon also by margaret wise brown a classic is eric carle's the very hungary catapillar and finally pat the bunny is a great book for babies it's an interactive book that allows babies to feel different textures on each page if you would like to continue getting your friend's baby books talk to other parents as to what the best books are you'll get a lot of wonderful titles giving the gift of reading is the best gift you can give Barnes & Noble Douglas Adams Infantilism Oxford English Dictionary Charmed The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe Bookbinding Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban The Beatles discography Baby Blues Knots Landing The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy The Catcher in the Rye About a Boy Kodocha Lord of the Flies Theory of conduct Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Jon Secada Book Wheel of Fortune Frankie Laine LiveJournal Social rule Caravan of Courage: An Ewok Adventure Gramophone record The Beach Boys Sharon Tate Roots: The Saga of an American Family Crazy in Love Mattress Captain Marvel (DC Comics) Cliff Richard Newbery Honor Peanuts Shaggy dog story Characters in the Smurfs Milton H. Erickson Transactional analysis Sailor Moon Advanced Squad Leader Kevin and Kell Ebook Homescho